Package com.jidesoft.tree

The package contains all kinds of components and classes based on JTree for JIDE Grids product.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
TreeModelWrapper TreeModelWrapper is a wrapper around tree model which is referred as the actual tree model or underlying tree model.
 

Class Summary
AbstractTreeModel This abstract class provides default implementations for some of the methods in the TreeModel interface.
DefaultTreeModelWrapper The default implementation of TreeModelWrapper.
FilterableCheckBoxTreeSelectionModel FilterableCheckBoxTreeSelectionModel is a subclass of CheckBoxTreeSelectionModel and use in CheckBoxTree to keep track of the checked tree paths.
FilterableTreeModel FilterableTreeModel is a TreeModelWrapper that can handle filters.
QuickTreeFilterField QuickTreeFilterField works along with any TreeModel to provide filtering feature.
SortableTreeModel SortableTreeModel is a tree model wrapper which can do the sorting.
StyledTreeCellRenderer A tree cell renderer based on StyledLabel.
TreeModelWrapperUtils TreeModelWrapperUtils is a utility class that contains several useful methods for TreeModelWrapper.
TreeSelectionModelGroup This class is used to create a multiple-exclusion scope for a set of TreeSelectionModel so that one TreeSelectionModel can have selected index at a time.
TreeShrinkSearchableSupport TreeShrinkSearchableSupport is a subclass of ShrinkSearchableSupport to make TreeSearchable shrinkable while searching.
